  <brief_title>Effect of Pulse Fractions on Indices on Cardiovascular Disease and Diabetes Risk Factors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Pulse Fractions on Indices of Lipid, Carbohydrate and Energy Metabolism as Well as Oxidative Status in Overweight, Hyperlipidemic Individuals</official_title>
