  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI between 25 and 40 kg/m2

          -  Hypercholesterolemic

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Smoking

          -  Use of prescription and natural lipid lowering therapies

          -  Myocardial infarction

          -  Coronary artery bypass

          -  Angina

          -  Congestive heart failure,

          -  Inflammatory bowel disease

          -  Pancreatitis

          -  Renal disease

          -  Diabetes

          -  Chronic alcohol usage (&gt; 2 drinks/day).

          -  Cancer

          -  Eating disorders

          -  Expending &gt; 4000 kcal/week through exercise
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
